    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action or process of conserving for the preservation of existence, state, life, health, safeguarding from destructive influences, natural decay, or waste. May apply to conserving a building, object, environment, species, or other thing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
